Usage: create_partition_wrapper [-help] -partitions <partition_names>
                                [-pushdown]
                                [-wrapper_name <wrapper_suffix_string>]

-help                                     # Prints out the command usage
-partitions <partition_names>             # Specifies the name of one or more
                                          # partition on which wrapper need to
                                          # be created (string, required)
-pushdown                                 # Keep the partition hinst intact for
                                          # wrapper partition (bool, optional)
-wrapper_name <wrapper_suffix_string>     # Specifies the suffix to be added to
                                          # wrapper partition name. Default is
                                          # ptnName_wrapper (string, optional)